    "description": "Dench, Grant, Mirren. Now try a new British favourite with this juicy twist on bangers 'n' mash. Pair your sausages with a rich onion marmalade gravy, green beans and roasted carrots for a dish worthy of a standing O. Finish your meal with a delicious chocolate pot!",
